{"tid":1834080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】麥理浩夫人度假村封營　預留作隔離中心 (15:39)","createTime":"2020-01-22T08:44:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T08:54:32.000Z","uid":40152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"99f50254e2f465e81b632b31af3c42e86e5ff70b","tid":1834080,"uid":40152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T08:44:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200122/s00001/f9b79870a0bb99283d366bf52e8c167f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200122%2Fs00001%2Ff9b79870a0bb99283d366bf52e8c167f.jpg&h=e405ba8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地新型冠狀病毒感染肺炎疫情持續擴大，網上流傳稱，為應對新型冠狀病毒肺炎，政府將徵用鯉魚門公園及麥理浩夫人度假村作隔離用途。本報記者今午（22日）致電麥理浩夫人度假村查詢，有職員表示，即日起已封閉營地，未來14日都不能入營，因為已預留用作隔離中心。本報亦向食衛局查詢，暫未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\n食衛局長陳肇始今早表示，康文署初步已預留兩個度假營，在有需要時隔離與患者有緊密接觸的人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200122/s00001/1579678637317/%e3%80%90%e6%ad%a6%e6%bc%a2%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e%e3%80%91%e9%ba%a5%e7%90%86%e6%b5%a9%e5%a4%ab%e4%ba%ba%e5%ba%a6%e5%81%87%e6%9d%91%e5%b0%81%e7%87%9f-%e9%a0%90%e7%95%99%e4%bd%9c%e9%9a%94%e9%9b%a2%e4%b8%ad%e5%bf%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200122%2Fs00001%2F1579678637317%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e6%25ad%25a6%25e6%25bc%25a2%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e%25e3%2580%2591%25e9%25ba%25a5%25e7%2590%2586%25e6%25b5%25a9%25e5%25a4%25ab%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e5%25ba%25a6%25e5%2581%2587%25e6%259d%2591%25e5%25b0%2581%25e7%2587%259f-%25e9%25a0%2590%25e7%2595%2599%25e4%25bd%259c%25e9%259a%2594%25e9%259b%25a2%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%25bf%2583&d=UWp4lduD54HchuVgBglmzUXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=67bf9964\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200122%2Fs00001%2F1579678637317%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e6%25ad%25a6%25e6%25bc%25a2%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e%25e3%2580%2591%25e9%25ba%25a5%25e7%2590%2586%25e6%25b5%25a9%25e5%25a4%25ab%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e5%25ba%25a6%25e5%2581%2587%25e6%259d%2591%25e5%25b0%2581%25e7%2587%259f-%25e9%25a0%2590%25e7%2595%2599%25e4%25bd%259c%25e9%259a%2594%25e9%259b%25a2%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%25bf%2583&h=e392ad4d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200122/s00001/1579678637317/%e3%80%90%e6%ad%a6%e6%bc%a2%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e%e3%80%91%e9%ba%a5%e7%90%86%e6%b5%a9%e5%a4%ab%e4%ba%ba%e5%ba%a6%e5%81%87%e6%9d%91%e5%b0%81%e7%87%9f-%e9%a0%90%e7%95%99%e4%bd%9c%e9%9a%94%e9%9b%a2%e4%b8%ad%e5%bf%83</a>"},{"pid":"318ff64b473947472f7b9f18bc74bd0da66471e3","tid":1834080,"uid":127791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T08:54:32.000Z","msg":"根本就知要大規模做隔離 呢個垃圾政府一定係後知後覺"}]}